author: RTÉ News
title: 'No evidence' of virus immunity in recovered patients
description: There is currently no evidence to support the belief that people who have recovered from coronavirus then have immunity, the World Health Organization has said.
content:
There is currently no evidence to support the belief that people who have recovered from coronavirus then have immunity, the World Health Organization has said.
